  beginOnStart: 1
  swapScene: 0
  sceneName: 
  audioSource: {fileID: 330722596}
  sceneManagey: {fileID: 330722594}
  text:
  - 'After your health decreased further than what it should, you were forced to
    be placed into a hospital. '
  - 'Due to not having any money, you were not admitted to a good hospital. '
  - 'After the doctors realized you could not pay, they simply decided to take your
    organs and sell them to pay for your medical bills.  '
  - 'The problem was they did not care about which organ they removed, which led
    to your death. '
  - 'The doctors decided to keep the sold organ money for themselves.  '
  - '*Dead End Unlocked* '
  whoIsTalking:
  - The Voice
  - The Voice
  - The Voice
  - The Voice
